2026-05-13T21:32:33.9423578Z 243            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-13T21:32:33.9424494Z 244            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-13T21:32:33.9425368Z 245            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-13T21:32:33.9426256Z 246            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-13T21:32:33.9427026Z 247            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-13T21:32:33.9427783Z 248            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-13T21:32:33.9428655Z 249            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-13T21:32:33.9429515Z 250            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
2026-05-13T21:32:33.9430376Z 251            crash report tagged "ProxyBillingActivity NPE" for context.
